Package org.hova.hover.sdk.http

Class Summary
ClientDELETE Creates a correct DELETE HTTP request with a json encoded as a body.
ClientGET Creates a correct GET HTTP request using query string as API needs.
ClientPOST Creates a correct POST HTTP request with a json encoded as a body.
ClientPUT Creates a correct PUT HTTP request with a json encoded as a body.
Response HTTP Code and Body as the API responses on the requested resource.
